    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep luster and no chips, scratches, or dings of any kind. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the leather remains supple, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic component functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in peak performance, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in like-new condition, ideal for a collector or a discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
